name: Dyna, Champion of the Skyfang Brigade
desc: If this card is Special Summoned: You can banish cards from your opponent's GY, up to the number of "Skyfang Brigade" monsters you control with different names. You can only use this effect of "Dyna, Champion of the Skyfang Brigade" once per turn. Your opponent's monsters cannot target "Skyfang Brigade" monsters for attacks, except this one.
